column15: Older brother distanced himself and started using drugs
Family contributed to anxiety; plucked eyelashes/eyebrows starting in 4th grade
Hid school problems from mom; disconnected from family
Became irritable and preoccupied with food and calories
Would restore and lose weight to make parents feel bad
Readmitted to inpatient psychiatric hospital after relapse
Not knowing how to express feelings
Hard when brother left for school
Injury in 9th grade - could not do sports
Quit attending school- had tutors for 4months
Family dynamics were poor, lots of fighting
Relapsed eating disorder and high anxiety
